headline: New report from Oliver Wyman and Association of Equipment Manufacturers finds rising uncertainty is reshaping equipment manufacturing
summary: NEW YORK, December 03, 2025--Oliver Wyman, a global leader in management consulting and a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE:MMC), and the Association of Equipment Manufacturers (AEM) today unveiled findings from a joint study on the state of the North America’s industrial goods sector, focusing on construction and agricultural manufacturing.
